The lightweight formula melts into skin with the consistency of creamy water and delivers buildable medium to full coverage, while light reflecting ingredients neutralize imperfections and create a soft focus effect with a natural finish. Magic Touch Concealer helps to hydrate the delicate under eye area and provides smooth, creaseless, and comfortable wear without oxidizing or settling into fine lines. Amino acid coated pigments ensure immediate adhesion and easy, flexible blendability.

4-chunk_376_3718054688898425609.chunk_text: Image 320: Get the Look: Blended & Blurred Complexion https://www.anastasiabeverlyhills.com/cdn/shop/articles/010225 MetaObject Article Frame Perfectly Blend and Blurred Foundatio a994edaa 39c8 411d 9e5e 3c7860a618f5. jpg? v 1746722837&width 600 face Get the Look: Blended & Blurred Complexion A blended and blurred look is where makeup has invisibly melted seamlessly into your skin, creating a smooth, even finish where imperfections, lines and texture have disappeared. It’s a wonderfully natural looking “soft focus” appearance that is always appealing, always flattering.

4-chunk_377_875028470445817675.chunk_text: It’s a wonderfully natural looking “soft focus” appearance that is always appealing, always flattering. And it’s surprisingly easy to create, if you know how. The key is new Impeccable Blurring Second Skin Matte Foundation from Anastasia Beverly Hills. Step1: Prime Start by prepping your skin with your favorite skincare or primer.

4-chunk_378_-5439831331029835648.chunk_text: Step1: Prime Start by prepping your skin with your favorite skincare or primer. If you have dry skin, we recommend making our Hydrating Oil part of your routine. Then apply 1 2 pumps of Impeccable Blurring Second Skin Matte Foundation, starting in the center of your face and working outward. Blend with A30 Pro Brush in circular motions to a seamless finish.

4-chunk_379_548249513538023215.chunk_text: Blend with A30 Pro Brush in circular motions to a seamless finish. Focus on desired areas to build coverage, using pressing motions to massage the product into your skin. Step 2: Perfect Next, let’s brighten and conceal any visible imperfections with Magic Touch Concealer. Using the wand, apply directly under the eyes, over blemishes or discoloration – anywhere you want extra coverage.

4-chunk_380_-1616300310975555600.chunk_text: Using the wand, apply directly under the eyes, over blemishes or discoloration – anywhere you want extra coverage. Start with a light layer and build as desired. Blend and diffuse using Brush 18 or tap with your fingertips using gentle pressure. To cover blemishes, select the shade closest to your natural skin tone.

4-chunk_381_4801500915875687708.chunk_text: To cover blemishes, select the shade closest to your natural skin tone. To neutralize redness, select a shade with a golden undertone. Step 3: Set Finally, set your new look with Impeccable 24HR Blurring Matte Setting Spray to blur and mattify for a long wearing finish. Shake the bottle before use.

4-chunk_382_-2180073026495806712.chunk_text: Shake the bottle before use. Hold it 6 8 inches away from your face and mist 2 4 times over in an X and T pattern so you coat the skin evenly. Be sure to keep it out of your eyes! For an extra locked in look, finish with Loose Setting Powder – this lightweight, silky formula is wonderfully blendable and sets makeup with a smooth, matte finish.

4-chunk_383_-7161143124472569615.chunk_text: For an extra locked in look, finish with Loose Setting Powder – this lightweight, silky formula is wonderfully blendable and sets makeup with a smooth, matte finish. 4-chunk_384_-6764939067854119412.chunk_text: jpg? v 1747920992&width 600 face Get the Look: Blurred & Matte Complexion It’s easy to achieve a smooth, flawless looking complexion when you know the proper techniques – just follow these tips from Anastasia Beverly Hills. Even if you have skin that sometimes looks oily or greasy, the blurred and matte complexion look is ideal for all skin types, with medium to full coverage to blur and conceal imperfections. Step 1: Perfect First, let’s blur and perfect your complexion with our new Impeccable Blurring Second Skin Matte Foundation for flawless looking skin.

4-chunk_385_-4715004511753956465.chunk_text: Step 1: Perfect First, let’s blur and perfect your complexion with our new Impeccable Blurring Second Skin Matte Foundation for flawless looking skin. Use 1 to 2 pumps of this liquid foundation and apply, starting in the center of the face and working outwards. The A30 Pro Brush is best for this. Blend in circular motions for a seamless finish, and build using stippling motions to your desired coverage.

4-chunk_386_-7009490779862852729.chunk_text: Blend in circular motions for a seamless finish, and build using stippling motions to your desired coverage. If you have oily skin, pair with Loose Setting Powder for best results. Step 2: Brighten Next, we’ll brighten and conceal with Magic Touch Concealer. Select a shade that is one or two shades lighter than your foundation to brighten.

4-chunk_387_4192685703223911837.chunk_text: Select a shade that is one or two shades lighter than your foundation to brighten. Apply directly under the eyes, over blemishes or discoloration – anywhere you want extra coverage. Start with a light layer and build as desired. Blend and diffuse using Brush 18 or tap with your fingertips using gentle pressure.

4-chunk_388_-6538732058837789305.chunk_text: Blend and diffuse using Brush 18 or tap with your fingertips using gentle pressure. Step 3: Finish Finally, let’s finish and intensify your look with Impeccable 24HR Blurring Setting Spray. Shake the bottle before use, then hold it 6 8 inches away from your face and mist 2 4 times over in an X and T pattern so you coat the skin evenly. Do be sure to keep it out of your eyes, of course.

4-chunk_389_-4170250343603792619.chunk_text: Do be sure to keep it out of your eyes, of course. Add This Want more radiant color in your complexion? Blurring Serum Blush will add a nice flushed from within look while treating your face with skin loving Niacinamide and Pomegranate Peels Extract. 4-chunk_396_-725662688063767406.chunk_text: Even when your plans are more staycation than vacation, you can achieve a wonderful sun worshipping look with little effort and barely there makeup. Step 1:Perfect First, we’ll brighten and conceal with Magic Touch Concealer. Using the wand, apply dots to the forehead, cheeks, nose and chin. Blend and diffuse using A30 Pro Brush.

4-chunk_397_-6367759845268786748.chunk_text: Blend and diffuse using A30 Pro Brush. Use stippling motions to build coverage. Step 2: Warm Next, add instant warmth and definition with Cream Bronzer. 4-chunk_398_943711369128214875.chunk_text: Use A30 Pro Brush to gently pick up a small amount of product and apply it using light pressure to your cheekbones, temples, forehead and jawline. Step 3: Radiate Finally, add a natural looking flush of color with Blurring Serum Blush – while also treating your face with skin loving niacinamide and pomegranate peels extract! Apply it directly to your cheeks; one dot is enough for a natural flush, two or three dots will give you more color intensity.

4-chunk_399_5263828388568738607.chunk_text: Apply it directly to your cheeks; one dot is enough for a natural flush, two or three dots will give you more color intensity. 4-chunk_421_-5622930166555756551.chunk_text: It’s easy to create this soft, slightly matte, slightly radiant and so on trend look at home. It’s great for all skin types – especially those with oily skin – and it goes with all makeup styles, from subtle to ultra glam. All you need is to follow these steps and use these makeup products from Anastasia Beverly Hills. Here’s how to do it.

4-chunk_422_6877271503223861167.chunk_text: Here’s how to do it. STEP 1: PERFECT Magic Touch Concealer To start, use creamy Magic Touch Concealer to correct and brighten your skin to an even, luminous finish. Select the shade closest to your skin tone, then use the wand to apply dots to the forehead, cheeks, nose and chin. Also apply directly over blemishes, discoloration, or anywhere you need extra coverage.

4-chunk_423_-1115399418365046847.chunk_text: Also apply directly over blemishes, discoloration, or anywhere you need extra coverage. Blend using the A30 Pro Brush. STEP 2: RADIANCE Blurring Serum Blush Next, we’ll add a natural looking flash of color using Blurring Serum Blush. This hydrating, soft matte liquid blush is great for creating the flushed from within effect that goes with this look.

4-chunk_424_-42275548295781935.chunk_text: This hydrating, soft matte liquid blush is great for creating the flushed from within effect that goes with this look. To apply, squeeze a dot directly onto the cheeks and blend with your fingertips, using gentle pressing motions. Add another dot or two if you want more intensity, or layer two shades to create a custom effect. STEP 3: SET Loose Setting Powder To finish, we’ll use Loose Setting Powder to brighten and blur.

4-chunk_425_-6923844057313554078.chunk_text: STEP 3: SET Loose Setting Powder To finish, we’ll use Loose Setting Powder to brighten and blur. This lightweight, silky powder sets makeup with the desired smooth, flawless matte finish you want. Apply using a makeup sponge or powder brush, lightly pressing in the areas you want to set. Be sure to focus on the T zone from forehead down to nose and chin, and under the eyes.

4-chunk_426_2833141907702424416.chunk_text: Be sure to focus on the T zone from forehead down to nose and chin, and under the eyes. You’re looking for a bright, diffused effect to achieve this look. 5-chunk_68_-3838181226082712948.chunk_text: Layer the shades in this pink toned Anastasia Glow Kit® together or wear separately on the face, eyes, lips https://www.anastasiabeverlyhills.com/collections/lips)and body. Highlighters can be applied wet or dry for true versatility in makeup application. For a natural looking glow, tap a makeup brush https://www.anastasiabeverlyhills.com/collections/makeup-brushes)like A23 Pro Brush https://www.anastasiabeverlyhills.com/products/a23 large tapered blending brush on the powder and then sweep over the high points of the face. For an intense glow, gently push the fibers of A23 Pro Brush into the powder and use a stippling motion to apply to the high points of the face—including the tops of the cheeks, bridge and tip of the nose, Cupid's bow, chin, inner corners of the eyes and brow bone.

5-chunk_69_928135340823750405.chunk_text: For an intense glow, gently push the fibers of A23 Pro Brush into the powder and use a stippling motion to apply to the high points of the face—including the tops of the cheeks, bridge and tip of the nose, Cupid's bow, chin, inner corners of the eyes and brow bone. For a sun kissed touch of color, apply the pink lilac shade Gumdrop to the apples of the cheeks. The deepest shade Butterscotch adds warmth and shape to the perimeter of the face, nose and cheeks.

12-chunk_144_595655480642202188.chunk_text: description The go to face and body foundation for House of Dior runway shows, Dior Backstage Face & Body Foundation offers luminous results and a custom coverage effect, from the most natural glow to a high perfection complexion. It immediately evens out and smooths the complexion, and blurs imperfections for a weightless, second skin finish. Imperceptible and comfortable, the ultra fine texture of this liquid foundation blends seamlessly with the skin upon application for long lasting wear that withstands extreme conditions: exercise, contact with water, high temperatures and damp environments.

12-chunk_145_9208500250561267721.chunk_text: Imperceptible and comfortable, the ultra fine texture of this liquid foundation blends seamlessly with the skin upon application for long lasting wear that withstands extreme conditions: exercise, contact with water, high temperatures and damp environments. Composed of 94% natural origin ingredients, the formula of the foundation is infused with plant derived squalane and hyaluronic acid. Non comedogenic, Dior Backstage Face & Body Foundation hydrates the skin all day long. Test performed between 25 30°C with 30 40% humidity.

The foundation ensures a long wearing makeup result and day long hydration thanks to the squalane and hyaluronic acid complex in the formula.
